
1. Getting the client:

   a. On Linux, "yum install bittorrent"
   b. On FreeBSD, install the /usr/ports/net/py-bittorrent port

2. Run as follows. Parameters below are suitable for this network's
   bandwidth and natd.conf setup:

   $ btdownloadcurses.py --max_allow_in 10 --max_initiate 10 -minport 6881 --maxport 6889 torrentfile
